  "text": "where f is the frequency of the vortex shedding. In figure 20 , where the evolutions of the drag and the lift coefficients according to the non dimensional time are presented, a periodic behavior of these coefficients can be noticed. The average drag coefficient C Dave , the root mean square of the lift coefficient C Lrms , and the Strouhal number were compared with experimental results found in the literature [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , and with numerical results obtained with the finite volume method (FVM), and more particularly with the OpenFOAM [43] code, on a structured mesh. In ",
